extends java.lang.Object
implements SPBrandEngageClientStatusListener

    Wrapper calls to perform a BrandEngage request and to notify a SPBrandEngageClientStatusListener of the result

    This class is not intended to be used directly or subclassed, it is used internally by SponsorPayPublisher
